If I lived in Singapore I'd buy from here

I built this out from scratch with their advice.

text.text: This is a proper aquarium shop with lots of offerings. Very happy with the attentive service. I also realized how important good lighting is to make your tank look super vibrant. Set it up with a timer so it doesn‚Äôt get too much light and have algae explosion.

text.text: Extremely reliable shop with top notch service, staff are very knowledgeable and patient as well. After sales service is also solid. Despite being mostly a freshwater fish store, they helped me set up my saltwater tank and have a wide product list for anyone setting up a reef tank. Wife has also been a regular here for her freshwater units. Essentially, everything from our filters to lights have been purchased from here. Reef rocks were from elsewhere, but everything else can be found here or their online store. 100% would recommend.

I have recently upgraded my tank and changed to external filter, week Aqua light with co2 set up  in which I don‚Äôt have any knowledge.
